OL,3,CSustainable clothing event in Penrith
OL,4,Chopes to reduce landfill
OL,6,FAn event has been held in Cumbria
OL,7,Faimed at improving sustainability in
OL,8,Ffashion. The Rewear Revolution hopes
OL,9,Fto reduce the 60,000 tonnes of clothes
OL,10,Fthat end up in landfill every year.
OL,12,FIt was organised by the Cumbria
OL,13,FClothing Collective and Restore
OL,14,FCumbria, with the message: rewear;
OL,15,Frecycle - not landfill and fast
OL,16,Ffashion.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
