PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1772467872
OL,3,CSustainable clothing event in Penrith
OL,4,Chopes to reduce landfill
OL,6,FRestore Cumbria works with charity
OL,7,Fshops, but, as their General Manager
OL,8,FFinn Wildhill explains, they actually
OL,9,Fdon't want clothes to end up there.
OL,10,FThey would rather we fix our clothes
OL,11,Fand keep them for longer.
OL,13,FMr Wildhill told ITV Border, "We see
OL,14,Fhuge amounts of waste from fast
OL,15,Ffashion brands that come through our
OL,16,Fdoors. Standard low cost brands only
OL,17,Flast maybe 6 or 7 washes before they
OL,18,Fhave to be thrown away, which means
OL,19,Fwhen they come to charity shops, we
OL,20,Fcan't sell them."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
