FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1772467872
OL,3,CSustainable clothing event in Penrith
OL,4,Chopes to reduce landfill
OL,6,FRestore Cumbria says they move about
OL,7,F25 tonnes of clothing waste a year,
OL,8,Fwhich is on the smaller end.
OL,10,FThe event on Saturday 28 February at
OL,11,Fthe Rheged Centre in Penrith had a
OL,12,Fsustainable fashion show with children
OL,13,Fand young people from seven schools
OL,14,Ffrom across Cumbria who made their own
OL,15,Foutfit. Mr Wildhill says "They want to
OL,16,Ftalk about circular economy. It's my
OL,17,Fgeneration we need to talk to, really."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
